<paragraph blockId="1.[674,1210,787,1066]" box="[677,777,787,813]" pageId="1" pageNumber="30">REMARKS</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[674,1210,787,1066]" pageId="1" pageNumber="30">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Brolemann" authorityYear="1931" box="[677,790,818,844]" class="Diplopoda" family="Lophoproctidae" genus="Lophoturus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Polyxenida" pageId="1" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[677,790,818,844]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="30">Lophoturus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as reassessed by Condé &amp; Nguyen Duy- Jacquemin (1977: 909-911), is a senior synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="Jeekel, 1963" authorityName="Jeekel" authorityYear="1963" box="[675,947,881,907]" genus="Alloproctinus" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="1" pageNumber="30" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[675,810,881,907]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="30">Alloproctinus</emphasis>
Jeekel, 1963
</taxonomicName>
(a replacement name for 
<taxonomicName authority="Silvestri, 1948" authorityName="Silvestri" authorityYear="1948" box="[675,952,913,939]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Alloproctus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[675,788,913,939]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="30">Alloproctus</emphasis>
Silvestri, 1948
</taxonomicName>
). It is characterized by 0 to 4 pairs of linguiform processes on each side of median opening of labrum and antennal article VI with 3 thick sensilla, named anterior (a) intermediate (i) and posterior (p) (
<bibRefCitation author="ISHII K. &amp; JACQUEMIN M." box="[903,1132,1039,1066]" pageId="1" pageNumber="30" pagination="239 - 267" refId="ref5452" refString="ISHII K., NGUYEN DUY- JACQUEMIN M. &amp; CONDE, B., 1999. - The first penicillate millipedes from the vicinity of Manaus, Central Amazonia, Brazil (Diplopoda: Polyxenida). Amazoniana 15 (3 / 4): 239 - 267." type="journal article" year="1999">
Ishii 
<emphasis box="[959,1010,1039,1065]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="30">et al.</emphasis>
1999: 252
</bibRefCitation>
, key).
</paragraph>
